title: Arvind Kejriwal, Bhagwant Mann spin charkha at Sabarmati Ashram ahead of Gujarat polls | Pics - India Today
content: Arvind Kejriwal, Bhagwant Mann spin charkha at Sabarmati Ashram ahead of Gujarat polls | Pics  India TodayView Full coverage on Google News
description: Ahead of the Gujarat Assembly election to be held later this year, AAP leaders Bhagwant Mann and Arvind Kejriwal visited the Sabarmati Ashram in Ahmedabad on Saturday.
